* Russian Federation, 1995
* South Africa, 1995
* Spain, 1990
* Sweden, 1991
* Switzerland, 1992
* Turkey, 1997
* Ukraine, 1998
* United Kingdom, 1987
* United States, 1987

Non-members pledging to adhere to MTCR include:

* China, 2002
* Israel
* Romania
* Slovakia
